channel.title: Anybody good with guis?
channel.description:
Hey im making a control panel, and i started from almost scratch... Lol, i have been learning slowly about how guis work, but ive come across a problem, whenever i press a button like "ban, mute, kill, pm" etc.. It gives runserver.bat errors, i have 2 things that work though, the "kick" command buton and the global message sending button. The problem i think is that it doesnt read like "c." before the int to make it work properly.
If anybody here can help me with my control panel, pm me or post here or add my skype : skype name : keithewewew35
